field.value:
Given:

{code}
public class IFoo { }

public class IBar { }

public class FooImpl : IFoo { }
{code}

Registrations that UseFactoryMethod() doesn't work with the proxy, for example:

{code}
container.Register(
    Component.For<IFoo>()
             .UsingFactoryMethod(kernal => new FooImpl())
             .Proxy.AddAdditionalInterfaces(typeof(IBar))
);
{code}

This however, works just fine:

{code}
container.Register(
    Component.For<IFoo>()
             .ImplementedBy<FooImpl>()
             .Proxy.AddAdditionalInterfaces(typeof(IBar))
);
{code}
